headline: 3 Consumer Stocks We’re Skeptical Of
summary: Most consumer discretionary businesses succeed or fail based on the broader economy. Lately, it seems like demand trends have worked in their favor as the industry has returned 33.1% over the past six months, outpacing S&P 500 by 8.4 percentage points.
